		<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, You can contact us:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<p>By email: <a href="mailto:timothy@kicksware.com">timothy@kicksware.com</a></p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<p>By visiting <a asp-controller="Contact" asp-action="Contact" rel="external nofollow noopener" target="_blank">this page on our website</a></p>
			</li>
		</ul>
		<p>Last updated: September 16, 2020</p>
	</div>
</div>